name: Marita visits twistedvizuals (doctagonz x nadie collaboration)
description: Marita visits twistedvizuals, or the art of doctagonz. This is the 1st collaboration with nadie (twitter: @ningunartista) I am a fan of Masita and thought it would be fun to see Marita trip out at my art. Nadie is a artist from colombia. May this collaboration bring you joy.
